# .gitmodules
# Removed hc-merge-pr35 submodule entry to avoid CI checkout errors
# If this repository needs submodules, re-add entries with proper 'url = ...' lines.
# Example entry format (commented):
# [submodule "some-submodule"]
# 	path = some-submodule
# 	url = https://github.com/owner/some-submodule.git

# Intentionally left empty to avoid malformed submodule entries causing
# `fatal: No url found for submodule path 'hc-merge-pr35' in .gitmodules` during CI.
